{"id":7842,"date":"2024-01-16T14:50:29","date_gmt":"2020-04-16T09:20:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7842"},"modified":"2024-10-19T21:51:43","modified_gmt":"2024-10-19T16:21:43","slug":"modern-minimalist-kitchen-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-minimalist-kitchen-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Simplicity At Its Best: A Modern Minimalist Kitchen Design"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>Anchor:\u00a0<\/strong>Shonali AdvaniIs <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Simplicity bliss for you? If you like to keep things simple and clutter-free, then check this modern minimalistic kitchen design showcased at\u00a0<\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"><em>DesignCafe\u2019s<\/em><\/a><em>\u00a0experience centre Mumbai.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Simplicity boils down to two steps: Identify the essential Eliminate the rest There is beauty in simplicity, it\u2019s a key to brilliance and ultimate sophistication. Not everyone wants a super posh kitchen with a glam factor. Some prefer a minimalistic kitchen that\u2019s simple and sweet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Is A Minimalistic Kitchen?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A minimalist kitchen is one which goes by its name minimal whether it be in its appearance or style. Minimalistic kitchens are designed to give you a clutter-free experience when you are in your kitchen cooking or simply baking around. Minimalistic kitchen is all about subtracting the obvious and adding the meaningful.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bit Of Modern, A Bit Of Minimalistic Kitchen Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Having a modern minimalist kitchen design means being a tad different from the mundane crowd with a combination of both modern and minimalist. Adding a touch of minimalism to a&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-kitchen-design\/\">modern kitchen design<\/a>&nbsp;can change how your kitchen looks. This kitchen uses the colour white in abundance as white is known to create an illusion for extra space. The cabinets and shelves are all in the shade white and to add a bit of modern magic, a lovely pop of lilac and indigo are integrated into the interiors. A seamless countertop in grey is simple and effortless, that sticks to the definition of being minimalist.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Minimalist Kitchen With Stunning Storage Options&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern minimalist kitchen interior design includes a tall unit with open bottle storage to keep your beloved booze at secured height. For those of you who love to add a bit of sugar and spice this minimalistic kitchen comes with a cosario unit. Now you can organise your spices in the order you like. This kitchen also has a push to open a wall unit that makes storage and access to crockery and goods easy. You literally push to open!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bakers Get Baking With Inbuilt This Baking Unit!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love baking but are worried about an oven taking up your space, time to chuck away your fear. This modern minimalistic kitchen has an inbuilt oven and microwave storage space that is carefully constructed below the open bottle storage unit. Let\u2019s bake already!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Simple Seamless Slab&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A neat and seamless slab is super important. To provide you with a hassle-free cooking experience this modern minimalist kitchen design comes with a grey granite slab with plenty of space around it. You can use it to stock up jars with your favourite pasta\u2019s, jams, biscuits, cereals, teabags or simply make it a place where you stir up some magic. So what\u2019s cooking tonight? Modern minimalist kitchen designs are becoming more popular among families of all kinds as this type of kitchen is pretty easy to maintain and doesn\u2019t compromise on storage and slab space. With a twist of modernness, this kitchen is a must-have for those of you who love a clean clutter-free cooking space. Did you enjoy DesignsCafe\u2019s video on Modern minimalist kitchens? Let us know! Leave your suggestions in the comments section below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about modern minimalist kitchen designs, also explore\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-organisation-ideas\/\">10 Kitchen Organisation Ideas.<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Anchor:\u00a0Shonali AdvaniIs Simplicity bliss for you? If you like to keep things simple and clutter-free, then check this modern minimalistic kitchen design showcased at\u00a0DesignCafe\u2019s\u00a0experience centre Mumbai. Simplicity boils down to two steps: Identify the essential Eliminate the rest There is beauty in simplicity, it\u2019s a key to brilliance and ultimate sophistication. Not everyone wants a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":28,"featured_media":7849,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":"","_wp_rev_ctl_limit":""},"categories":[9],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-7842","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-modular-kitchen-interiors","8":"typeofpost-video-blog"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Modern Minimalist Kitchen Designs For Your Home<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"T